title: OnePlus 10 Pro officially expands to US, Europe, and other global marks from $899
content:
The OnePlus 10 Pro officially made its debut back in January, but the phone was limited to China at first. Today, OnePlus is officially launching the OnePlus 10 Pro globally, with the phone extending to the United States, Europe, India, and other countries around the world.

description: After a three-month period being exclusive to China, the OnePlus 10 Pro has been officially announced for the US and other global markets.
